---
---
<section class="layout bound-x scheme-default py-[32px] m-0 border-0 transition-colors duration-300">
  <div class="max-w-screen-vp10 mx-auto mb-16 text-center">
    <span class="typo-label text-[var(--scheme-accent)] mb-4 block transition-colors duration-300">Their words, not ours</span>
    <h2 class="typo-h2 transition-colors duration-300">Proof in practice</h2>
  </div>
  
  <div class="grid vp7:grid-cols-2 vp9:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-left">
      <div class="bg-[var(--scheme-shade)] border border-[var(--scheme-border)] p-10 rounded-3xl flex flex-col gap-6 shadow-sm dark:shadow-none hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
         <div class="text-[var(--scheme-accent)] opacity-60 mb-2 transition-colors duration-300">
           <svg width="40" height="40" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
         </div>
         <p class="typo-p flex-grow font-medium transition-colors duration-300">"Timefold allowed us to reduce our fleet operations planning from hours to minutes, securing unparalleled efficiency across all branches."</p>
         <div class="pt-6 border-t border-blue-100 dark:border-white/5 mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-full transition-colors duration-300"></div>
            <div>
               <p class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-bold text-sm transition-colors duration-300">VP of Logistics</p>
               <div class="text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300">Enterprise Corp</div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-[var(--scheme-shade)] border border-[var(--scheme-border)] p-10 rounded-3xl flex flex-col gap-6 shadow-sm dark:shadow-none hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
         <div class="text-[var(--scheme-accent)] opacity-60 mb-2 transition-colors duration-300">
           <svg width="40" height="40" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
         </div>
         <p class="typo-p flex-grow font-medium transition-colors duration-300">"Deploying the shift scheduling API was incredibly fast. Our developers loved the clear documentation and immediate ROI."</p>
         <div class="pt-6 border-t border-blue-100 dark:border-white/5 mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 transition-colors duration-300">
             <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-full transition-colors duration-300"></div>
             <div>
                <p class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-bold text-sm transition-colors duration-300">Chief Technology Officer</p>
                <div class="text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300">Health Systems</div>
             </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-[var(--scheme-shade)] border border-[var(--scheme-border)] p-10 rounded-3xl flex flex-col gap-6 shadow-sm dark:shadow-none hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300">
         <div class="text-[var(--scheme-accent)] opacity-60 mb-2 transition-colors duration-300">
           <svg width="40" height="40" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
         </div>
         <p class="typo-p flex-grow font-medium transition-colors duration-300">"Complex constraints like driver skills and union rules were matched flawlessly out of the box. Highly recommended platform."</p>
         <div class="pt-6 border-t border-blue-100 dark:border-white/5 mt-auto flex items-center gap-4 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-200 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-full transition-colors duration-300"></div>
            <div>
               <p class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-bold text-sm transition-colors duration-300">Director of Operations</p>
               <div class="text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm tracking-wide transition-colors duration-300">City Transit</div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
